Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:06.060
In my last video we performed an experiment
in which two identical wood blocks were shot

00:00:06.060 --> 00:00:09.990
with the same rifle, one through the center
of mass and the other one slightly off to

00:00:09.990 --> 00:00:10.990
one side.

00:00:10.990 --> 00:00:14.420
Now if you haven’t seen that video yet,
